210
00:16:30,654 --> 00:16:33,934
Mi Mi, we have to go to the hospital. Let's go.

211
00:16:33,934 --> 00:16:35,674
No need, Big Sister Xin Ran.

212
00:16:35,674 --> 00:16:38,594
I'll be fine after I take medicine and sleep.

213
00:16:38,594 --> 00:16:40,894
You can't just take medicine for such a severe fever.

214
00:16:40,894 --> 00:16:43,594
Mi Mi, listen to me,

215
00:16:44,654 --> 00:16:47,676
