216
00:16:47,676 --> 00:16:49,754
No.

217
00:16:49,754 --> 00:16:51,960
Don't call him.

218
00:16:52,614 --> 00:16:54,954
He won't want to see me.

219
00:16:54,954 --> 00:16:57,054
After your fight,

220
00:16:57,994 --> 00:17:01,394
